name: WormArt - Kangaroo Island
description:
Original photography fed to the ravenous Algorithm Worms which secrete a delightful pigment trail as they happily writhe around the canvas.

Kangaroo Island is located just off the coast of South Australia near its capital Adelaide. It is the home to a variety of wildlife including penguins, albino kangaroos and more. This beach at Cape Willoughby is covered in red tinged rocks which have been worn smooth by being on the weather exposed coast of the island.

3000x3000.
